---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of service for our automated content generation website."
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mb-8">
        <p class="text-yellow-800">
          <strong>Important Notice:</strong> This is a template terms of service for an automated content website. 
          Consult with legal professionals to ensure compliance with applicable laws.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing and using this website, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. 
        If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use this website.
      </p>
      
      <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>
        This website provides automated content generation services. Content is created using artificial intelligence 
        systems and is intended for informational purposes only. We strive for accuracy but make no guarantees 
        regarding the completeness, reliability, or accuracy of this information.
      </p>
      
      <h2>3. Automated Content Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        All content on this website is generated through automated systems using artificial intelligence. 
        While we implement quality control measures, the content:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Is generated by algorithms, not human writers</li>
        <li>May contain inaccuracies or errors</li>
        <li>Should not be considered professional advice</li>
        <li>Should be verified with authoritative sources when accuracy is critical</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        The content, organization, graphics, design, compilation, and other matters related to this site are protected 
        under applicable copyrights and other proprietary laws. The copying, redistribution, use or publication by you 
        of any such matters or any part of the site is strictly prohibited.
      </p>
      
      <h2>5. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>As a user of this website, you agree to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the content for lawful purposes only</li>
        <li>Not attempt to interfere with the website's operation</li>
        <li>Not use automated systems to access the website excessively</li>
        <li>Acknowledge that content is AI-generated and verify important information</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        We shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential or punitive damages resulting from 
        your use or inability to use the service or for the unavailability of the service. We make no warranties 
        regarding the accuracy or completeness of any content.
      </p>
      
      <h2>7. Medical/Financial/Legal Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The content on this website is for informational purposes only and is not intended as medical, financial, 
        or legal advice. Always seek the advice of qualified professionals regarding medical conditions, financial 
        decisions, or legal matters.
      </p>
      
      <h2>8. External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain links to external websites. We have no control over the content and nature of these 
        sites and are not responsible for their content. The inclusion of any links does not necessarily imply 
        a recommendation or endorsement.
      </p>
      
      <h2>9. Advertisements</h2>
      <p>
        This website uses Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google uses cookies to serve ads based on your 
        prior visits to this website or other websites. You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting 
        Google's Ads Settings.
      </p>
      
      <h2>10. Termination</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to terminate your access to the website, without any advance notice, for any reason 
        including but not limited to violation of these Terms of Service.
      </p>
      
      <h2>11. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. We will notify users of any changes by updating 
        the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Your continued use of the website after any changes 
        constitutes acceptance of those changes.
      </p>
      
      <h2>12. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction where 
        the website operator is based, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.
      </p>
      
      <h2>13. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us through our contact page.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Summary of Key Points</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Content is AI-generated - verify important information</li>
          <li>Not professional advice - consult experts for critical matters</li>
          <li>Use content responsibly and legally</li>
          <li>We're not liable for damages from content use</li>
          <li>Ads are served by Google AdSense</li>
          <li>Terms may change - check back periodically</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">← Back to Home</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">View Privacy Policy →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>